  "body": "### Description\r\nWhen syncing and EL is offline we mark import batches to be invalid and drop peers.\r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/15999009/149928124-5dfd8dc9-79a6-4849-8b89-6b637325fa72.png)\r\n\r\n```\r\nMarking batch EventThreadOnlyBatch{delegate=SyncSourceBatch{firstSlot=203123, lastSlot=203172, count=50, complete=true, requiredParent=7409a3..e2c9, firstBlock=7b9bea..6155 (203124) (parent: 7409a3..e2c9), lastBlock=c650f3..ae62 (203172)}} as invalid because it extends from an invalid block\r\n```\r\n\r\nwe should better handle the situation.",
